        <h3 MadCap:conditions="LingoGuides.LingoWhatsNewGuide">Table Summary—Major New Features</h3>
        <p>Following are the <span class="EmphasisItalic">major</span> new features introduced in this version of <MadCap:snippetText src="../../AllProductVariables.flsnp" />. </p>
        <table class="TableStyle-BasicAlternateRows" style="margin-left: 0; margin-right: auto; mc-table-style: url('../../../TableStyles/BasicAlternateRows.css'); mc-table-style-original: url('../../../TableStyles/BasicAlternateRows.css');" cellspacing="0">
            <col class="TableStyle-BasicAlternateRows-Column-Regular" />
            <col class="TableStyle-BasicAlternateRows-Column-Regular" />
            <col class="TableStyle-BasicAlternateRows-Column-Regular" MadCap:conditions="" />
            <thead>
                <tr class="TableStyle-BasicAlternateRows-Head-Header1">
                    <th class="TableStyle-BasicAlternateRows-HeadD-Regular-Header1" colspan="3">
                        <p class="TableTextHead" style="text-align: left;">MAJOR NEW FEATURES</p>
                    </th>
                </tr>
                <tr class="TableStyle-BasicAlternateRows-Head-Header1">
                    <th class="TableStyle-BasicAlternateRows-HeadE-Regular-Header1">
                        <p class="TableTextHead">Feature</p>
                    </th>
